Okay cool thanks for letting me know!

history.content:
Are you interested in participating in a hackathon, but with startups? Do you want to develop a website or mobile app or work on a business/marketing plan? Are you a film, media content creator, or graphic designer looking for your next big project? Are you a student looking for your next job/internship?


Apply to be a part of LAUNCHATHON (March 16-17), a two-day event hosted by UC Berkeley’s LAUNCH Startup Accelerator program where you will work directly with a startup on a project and present your results at the end in a contest to win prizes ($500 top prize for each category). Depending on your skill set, we will match you with a startup who needs your skills the most, whether it be app software development or graphic design. The deadline to fill out the application at tinyurl.com/launchathon19 is Sunday, March 3rd at 11:59 PM.
history.subject: Launchathon Application 2019
